== English ==

=== Etymology ===

[[Portmanteau]] of ''[[white]]'' and ''[[nigger]]''.

=== Noun ===

'''wigger'''

# {{informal}} {{derogatory}} a [[white]] person (typically [[young]] and [[male]]) who dresses, speaks, or otherwise behaves in a manner that is stereotypically associated with certain aspects of African-American or Caribbean culture.